ðŸ› ï¸ 3. System/Website Implementation Plan (Simple Version)
Every question stored in DB should include:
{
  id: number,
  category: string,
  question_text: string,
  optionA: string,
  optionB: string,
  optionC: string,
  optionD: string,
  correctOption: "A/B/C/D",
  randomValuesUsed: {...},
}

Algorithm for Dynamic Questions

Select template based on category

Randomize numbers (e.g., side = random(2â€“20))

Compute correct answer

Generate distractors (based on common student errors)

Shuffle answer order

Return MCQ to user

Your system will produce thousands of unique questions automatically.

